  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This 3 weeks study examines the correlation between stress and alcohol using an ecological,
      prospective design.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This 3 weeks study examines the correlation between stress and alcohol using an ecological,
      prospective design. Participants will be given phone calls 4 times a day for 3 weeks,
      assessing perceived stress and alcohol related craving.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
